Author: drusenko
Title: Why you won't run out of money

Author: coffeeaddicted
Content: What I find more important now in retrospect is to agree upon a name as one of the first things when working together with someone. Not because the name is important, but because this will be the first decision where you can find out how good you will work together when you have an argument. If you can't decide on a name, work with someone else.\n
